     MOVE  "DSP-READ-SEC"        TO  S-NAME.
*
     MOVE  "NE"                  TO  DSP-PRO.
*
*    MOVE  "SCREEN"              TO  DSP-GRP.
     EVALUATE   PSW
*      曜日
       WHEN  "1"
         MOVE  "GPHEAD"          TO  DSP-GRP
*      明細
       WHEN  "2"
